      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_D2ABB2F0-083F-0135-B19C-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To open a discussion for comments, click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1] and click the <strong>Open for Comments</strong> link [2].</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> The same steps apply when opening comments in Discussions Redesign [3].</p>
  </div>
